"title": "4018: life, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4018",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Life embraces more than physical existence; it includes humanity's relationship with God. Human beings come to life spiritually only through faith in the redeeming work of God in Jesus Christ. This spiritual life is a foretaste of the life which believers will finally enjoy to the full in the new heaven and earth. Life in the Spirit means keeping in step with the promptings and guidance of the Holy Spirit, and always being open to his gifts and empowerment.</p>\n<h2>The nature of spiritual life</h2>\n<h3>It is new life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:20\">ACT 5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:18\">ACT 11:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:3\">2PE 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:14\">1JN 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>It is true life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:19</a></strong></p>\n<h3>It is eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:21\">ROM 5:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:27\">JHN 6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:11\">1JN 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>It is abundant life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:11\">PSA 16:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:8\">JER 17:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:3\">PSA 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:10\">JHN 10:10</a></p>\n<h2>The origins and nature of spiritual life</h2>\n<h3>Spiritual life is the work of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:6\">JHN 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:8\">JHN 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:26\">EZK 36:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:3\">JHN 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:5-John3:7\">JHN 3:5–3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:5–3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual life unites believers to Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:3-Rom6:5\">ROM 6:3–6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:10\">ROM 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13\">COL 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:12\">1JN 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual life makes believers the children of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:12-John1:13\">JHN 1:12–1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:20\">DEU 30:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:9\">MAT 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15\">ROM 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:18\">JAS 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7\">1JN 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:1\">1JN 5:1</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual life brings people to know God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:27\">MAT 11:27</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual life brings about faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:15\">JHN 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:31\">JHN 20:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:40\">JHN 6:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25\">JHN 11:25</a></p>\n<h2>Keeping in step with the Spirit</h2>\n<h3>A new way of life is made possible</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:25\">GAL 5:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:6\">ROM 8:5–8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:9-Rom8:16\">ROM 8:9–8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16-Gal5:18\">GAL 5:16–5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:24\">GAL 5:22–5:24</a></p>\n<h3>Bondage to the written law is ended</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:29\">ROM 2:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:6\">ROM 7:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:2\">ROM 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:6\">2CO 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:17-Gal5:18\">GAL 5:17–5:18</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience to God is made possible</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:4\">ROM 8:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:13\">ROM 8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16\">GAL 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:7-1Thess4:8\">1TH 4:7–4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Deepening unity is encouraged</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:3\">EPH 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13\">COL 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:4\">PHP 2:1–2:4</a></p>\n<h3>Strength and encouragement are received</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a></p>\n<h2>Gifts for those living in the Spirit</h2>\n<h3>Gifts are given for building up the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:4-1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:4–12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6-Rom12:8\">ROM 12:6–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:27-1Cor12:30\">1CO 12:27–12:30</a></p>\n<h3>Visions are given</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17\">ACT 2:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28\">JOL 2:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:10\">REV 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:12-Rev1:13\">REV 1:12–1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:2\">REV 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:3\">REV 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:10\">REV 21:10</a></p>\n<h3>Miracles are worked</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:28\">MAT 12:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:19\">ROM 15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:5\">GAL 3:5</a></p>\n<h3>Ministry is enhanced</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:6\">2CO 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:7-2Cor3:9\">2CO 3:7–3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Those living in the Spirit receive revelation and guidance</h2>\n<h3>God is revealed as Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14-Rom8:16\">ROM 8:14–8:16</a></p>\n<h3>God's purposes are revealed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:9-1Cor2:10\">1CO 2:9–2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:2-2Cor5:5\">2CO 5:2–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:5\">GAL 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17-Eph1:18\">EPH 1:17–1:18</a></p>\n<h3>Guidance is given to believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:29\">ACT 8:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:19\">ACT 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:12\">ACT 11:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">ACT 13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6-Acts16:7\">ACT 16:6–16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:22-Acts20:23\">ACT 20:22–20:23</a></p>\n<h3>Help is given to pray</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26-Rom8:27\">ROM 8:26–8:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:20\">JUD 1:20</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit sanctifies those in whom he lives</h2>\n<h3>Through the Spirit, Jesus Christ lives in believers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16-Eph3:17\">EPH 3:16–3:17</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit transforms believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:16\">ROM 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>The fruit of the Spirit is seen in believers' lives</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:52\">ACT 13:52</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6\">ROM 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:30\">ROM 15:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:8\">COL 1:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of life in the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1\">MAT 4:1</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:12\">MRK 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1\">LUK 4:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:18\">MAT 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:28\">MAT 12:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:14\">LUK 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">LUK 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:21\">LUK 10:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a></p>\n<h3>Simeon</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25-Luke2:27\">LUK 2:25–2:27</a></p>\n<h3>Peter</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:8\">ACT 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:19\">ACT 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:44\">ACT 10:44</a></p>\n<h3>Stephen</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:5\">ACT 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:10\">ACT 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:55\">ACT 7:55</a></p>\n<h3>The first Christians</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:3-Acts6:5\">ACT 6:3–6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:24\">ACT 11:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:27-Acts11:29\">ACT 11:27–11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:1-Acts13:3\">ACT 13:1–13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">ACT 15:28</a></p>",
